---
---
<section id="por-que-nexus" class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden bg-cosmos-dark border-t border-gray-800">
  <!-- Subtle star overlay -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-stars opacity-20 pointer-events-none"></div>
  
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      
      <!-- Left Column: Branding, Title, SVG Constellation -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 text-center lg:text-left flex flex-col items-center lg:items-start select-none">
        <h2 class="text-gold-deep text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4 text-glow">Filosofía de Trabajo</h2>
        <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-normal font-heading mb-8 text-white tracking-wide leading-tight">
          ¿Por qué <br class="hidden lg:block"/>
          <span class="italic text-gold-bright">Pegasus Nexus</span>?
        </h3>
        
        <!-- Celestial Connection SVG -->
        <div class="w-full max-w-[280px] p-4 bg-cosmos-light/20 border border-gray-800/40 rounded-none relative group mt-4">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" class="w-full h-auto text-gold-deep/40 group-hover:text-gold-deep/60 transition-colors duration-500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <!-- Outer circle network -->
            <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="80" stroke-dasharray="2 4" stroke-width="0.75" />
            <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="50" stroke-dasharray="1 5" stroke-width="0.75" />
            
            <!-- Network Nodes -->
            <circle cx="100" cy="20" r="3" fill="currentColor" />
            <circle cx="180" cy="100" r="3" fill="currentColor" />
            <circle cx="100" cy="180" r="3" fill="currentColor" />
            <circle cx="20" cy="100" r="3" fill="currentColor" />
            
            <circle cx="60" cy="60" r="4.5" fill="#F8FAFC" class="text-gold-bright" />
            <circle cx="140" cy="60" r="4.5" fill="#F8FAFC" class="text-gold-bright" />
            <circle cx="140" cy="140" r="4.5" fill="#F8FAFC" class="text-gold-bright" />
            <circle cx="60" cy="140" r="4.5" fill="#F8FAFC" class="text-gold-bright" />
            
            <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="6" fill="#3B82F6" class="text-cosmos-blue" />

            <!-- Connecting Lines -->
            <line x1="100" y1="20" x2="60" y2="60" />
            <line x1="100" y1="20" x2="140" y2="60" />
            <line x1="180" y1="100" x2="140" y2="60" />
            <line x1="180" y1="100" x2="140" y2="140" />
            <line x1="100" y1="180" x2="140" y2="140" />
            <line x1="100" y1="180" x2="60" y2="140" />
            <line x1="20" y1="100" x2="60" y2="140" />
            <line x1="20" y1="100" x2="60" y2="60" />

            <!-- Inner Connections (to center node) -->
            <line x1="60" y1="60" x2="100" y2="100" stroke-width="1.5" />
            <line x1="140" y1="60" x2="100" y2="100" stroke-width="1.5" />
            <line x1="140" y1="140" x2="100" y2="100" stroke-dasharray="2 2" />
            <line x1="60" y1="140" x2="100" y2="100" stroke-dasharray="2 2" />
            
            <!-- Additional cross links -->
            <line x1="60" y1="60" x2="140" y2="60" stroke-dasharray="3 3" />
            <line x1="60" y1="140" x2="140" y2="140" stroke-dasharray="3 3" />
          </svg>
          <!-- Subtle layout overlay styling matching the bento cards -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 border border-white/5 pointer-events-none"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Right Column: Manifesto text -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-7 flex flex-col justify-center space-y-8 text-left">
        
        <!-- Key statement quote block -->
        <div class="border-l-2 border-gold-deep/50 pl-6 py-2">
          <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-heading font-light text-white italic leading-relaxed">
            "No desarrollamos software por desarrollar."
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Explanation paragraph -->
        <p class="text-gray-300 font-montserrat font-light leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg">
          Combinamos experiencia en gestión empresarial, Business Intelligence, automatización e inteligencia artificial para diseñar soluciones que generan resultados medibles.
        </p>
        
        <!-- Stars/Constellation decorative line -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 py-2 opacity-50">
          <div class="h-px bg-gold-deep/30 flex-grow"></div>
          <span class="text-gold-deep text-sm">✦</span>
          <div class="h-px bg-gold-deep/30 flex-grow"></div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Structured points -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
          
          <!-- Point 1 -->
          <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
            <span class="text-gold-bright font-cinzel font-bold text-lg select-none">01.</span>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <h4 class="text-white font-montserrat font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">El Negocio Primero</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-400 font-montserrat font-light text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Nuestro enfoque no comienza con la tecnología. Comienza entendiendo el negocio.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Point 2 -->
          <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
            <span class="text-gold-bright font-cinzel font-bold text-lg select-none">02.</span>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <h4 class="text-white font-montserrat font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Decisiones sobre Sistemas</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-400 font-montserrat font-light text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Porque una empresa no necesita más sistemas. Necesita mejores decisiones.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
        </div>
        
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
